'''歌詩達迷人號'''（{{lang-en|'''Costa Fascinosa'''}}）是[[歌詩達郵輪船隊|歌詩達郵輪船隊]]擴充計劃，五艘船隻其中的一艘協和級郵輪，於2007年10月訂製，2012年5月6日首航。

==設計與建造==
歌詩達迷人號及其姊妹郵輪[[歌詩達輝宏號|歌詩達輝宏號]]，於2007年10月訂製，是歌詩達郵輪船隊24億歐元的擴充計劃的一部份，志在建造五艘全新的郵輪，並於2009年到2012年期間投入服務，令船隊的載客量提升50%。<ref name="Cruise Industry News">{{cite web |url=http://www.cruiseindustrynews.com/cruise-news/3347-11309-costa-favolosa-and-fascinosa.html |title=Costa Favolosa and Fascinosa |date=3 November 2010 |accessdate=16 February 2010 |work=Cruise Industry News |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cruiseindustrynews.com%2Fcruise-news%2F3347-11309-costa-favolosa-and-fascinosa.html&date=2012-11-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Niemela>{{cite news |url=http://www.cruisebusiness.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=932:costa-deliziosa-handed-over&catid=43:latest-news-catecory&Itemid=115 |title=Costa Deliziosa handed over |last=Niemelä |first=Teijo |date=31 January 2010 |work=Cruise Business Review |accessdate=16 February 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708212018/http://www.cruisebusiness.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=932%3Acosta-deliziosa-handed-over&catid=43%3Alatest-news-catecory&Itemid=115 |archive-date=2011-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 

兩艘船的名字均在比賽中挑選出來，第一階段已收到來自全球的16,000對提議，當中25對入圍的名字被放到公司網站上供大眾投票，最後選出''Fascinosa''和''Favolosa''，意大利語意思分別為美艷（"glamorous"）和極好（"fabulous"）。<ref name="Cruise Industry News"/>

船艦建基於協和級的設計<ref name=profile>{{cite web |url=http://www.costacruisesasia.com/B2C/AUS/Corporate/The+company/aboutourselves/aboutourselves.htm |title=Company profile |publisher=Costa Cruises |accessdate=16 February 2010 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.costacruisesasia.com%2FB2C%2FAUS%2FCorporate%2FThe%2Bcompany%2Faboutourselves%2Faboutourselves.htm&date=2012-11-19 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，[[排水量|排水量]]達114,500[[英噸|英噸]]<ref name="Cruise Industry News"/>，共提供1,506個客艙，可乘載3,780個客人<ref name="Cruise Industry News"/><ref name=orderPR>{{cite press release |title=Costa Crociere orders two new cruise ships from Fincantieri |publisher=Costa Cruises |date=18 October 2007 |url=http://www.costacruise.com/B2C/USA/Info/two_new_cruise_ship.htm |accessdate=16 February 2010 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.costacruise.com%2FB2C%2FUSA%2FInfo%2Ftwo_new_cruise_ship.htm&date=2012-11-19 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，是船隊的第十六艘船艦<ref name="Cruise Industry News"/>。

==運作簡史==
歌詩達迷人號主要於[[地中海|地中海]]東部航行<ref name="st">{{cite web | url=http://shipbuildingtribune.com/2012/05/07/italy-fincantieris-marghera-shipyard-delivers-costa-fascinosa/ | title=Italy: Fincantieri’s Marghera Shipyard Delivers Costa Fascinosa | publisher=Shipbuilding Tribune | date=7 May 2012 | accessdate=17 May 2012 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67ibAsxCN?url=http://shipbuildingtribune.com/2012/05/07/italy-fincantieris-marghera-shipyard-delivers-costa-fascinosa/ | archivedate=2012-05-17 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>， 2012年11月被調往南美洲，2013年夏季返回地中海服務<ref name="st"/>。

